Description: Implements models of chromosome number evolution similar to
    chromEvol using Markov and MuSSE models in the diversitree framework.
    Supports state-dependent chromosome evolution where a binary trait can
    affect rates of chromosome gain, loss, polyploidy, and demiploidy, as
    well as state-dependent speciation and extinction.
